{
  "stem": "18450.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 581.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they said if you want to stay here, you have to work on the cotton plantations.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Otherwise, you're on your own.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had no bread, no food, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even water then wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we went with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took us to a place on a plantation of cotton.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we stayed there because the first thing, we had no documents, nothing there from Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The second thing, the Germans were still coming further in Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So nobody bothered with nobody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They gave you a piece of bread once in two weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And before your time came in to go to this-- you know, to get your rationing, they were out of bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So there was nobody you could say anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was, you know, a chaos.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The hunger was bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People died of hunger more than of anything else, because it was hunger, no-- no soap.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The dirt was awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And over there, the water, it was coming from the mountains with all the dirt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they using like the water came from my house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had a canal to your house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You washed and everything in this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you drink the water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's why they always used to boil the water there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much, very much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was diarrhea, malaria, typhus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anything just mentioned, they had there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had medical care.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't inquire till I was in Namangan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It N-A-M-A-G-A-N.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The cotton plantation was near there, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and when you need it, you had to go into the city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a, like a doctor, I would say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's really a nurse practitioner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had in-- in every plantation, they had a nurse practitioner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the hospitals were all in the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
